[
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "p值补充 ",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            457,
            387,
            620
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$p$ 值的定义",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            91,
            142,
            325,
            244
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "CLASSICAL $p$ -VALUES ",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            243,
            300,
            452,
            344
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "The classical $p$ -value for the test statistic $T(y)$ is ",
        "bbox": [
            246,
            407,
            590,
            446
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\np _ {C} = \\Pr \\left(T (y ^ {\\text {r e p}}) \\geq T (y) | \\theta\\right).\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            405,
            500,
            605,
            544
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "The probability is taken over the distribution of $y^{\\mathrm{rep}}$ with $\\theta$ fixed. ",
        "bbox": [
            261,
            638,
            732,
            672
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "NOTE ",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            247,
            762,
            296,
            792
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "The distribution of $y^{\\mathrm{rep}}$ given $y$ and $\\theta$ is the same as its distribution given $\\theta$ alone. ",
        "bbox": [
            246,
            805,
            768,
            885
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "经典检验问题的 $p$ 值计算公式",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            144,
            719,
            244
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "已知 $y_{1}, \\ldots, y_{n} \\sim N(\\theta , 1)$ , 检验 $\\mathrm{H}_{0}$ : $\\theta = \\theta_{0}$ 。",
        "bbox": [
            89,
            320,
            595,
            381
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\triangleright y = \\left(y _ {1}, \\dots , y _ {n}\\right)\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            453,
            297,
            503
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$\\succ$ 统计量为 $T(y) = \\frac{\\bar{y} - \\theta_{0}}{1 / \\sqrt{n}}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            87,
            601,
            388,
            698
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "经典检验问题的 $p$ 值计算公式",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            144,
            719,
            244
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$p$ 值计算公式:",
        "bbox": [
            85,
            296,
            262,
            357
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} \\triangleright H _ {1} \\colon \\theta > \\theta_ {0} \\colon p _ {c} = P \\{N (0, 1) > T (y) \\} \\\\ \\triangleright H _ {1} \\colon \\theta <   \\theta_ {0} \\colon p _ {c} = P \\{N (0, 1) <   T (y) \\} \\\\ \\triangleright H _ {1} \\colon \\theta \\neq \\theta_ {0} \\colon p _ {c} = P \\{| N (0, 1) | > | T (y) | \\} = 2 P \\{N (0, 1) > | T (y) | \\} \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            414,
            902,
            707
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "若 $p_{c}< \\alpha$ （接近0），则拒绝 $\\mathrm{H}_{0}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            85,
            829,
            482,
            892
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "从 $y^{\\mathrm{rep}}$ 角度看 $p$ 值",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            144,
            463,
            244
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "假设 $\\mathrm{H}_{0}$ 成立, 即 $\\theta = \\theta_{0}$ , 亦即 $y_{1}, \\ldots, y_{n} \\sim N\\left(\\theta_{0}, 1\\right)$ 。",
        "bbox": [
            67,
            292,
            689,
            357
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "现从 $N(\\theta_0, 1)$ 中生成的重复数据（replicated data），记为 $y^{\\mathrm{rep}} = (y_1^{\\mathrm{rep}}, \\ldots, y_n^{\\mathrm{rep}})$ 。",
        "bbox": [
            67,
            479,
            929,
            646
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由于 $y ^{\\mathrm {r e p}}$ 与 $y$ 来自同一分布, 所谓 “同源”, 因此由 $y ^{\\mathrm {r e p}}$ 与 $y$ 应该 “相差无几”。",
        "bbox": [
            71,
            770,
            930,
            918
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "从 $y^{\\mathrm{rep}}$ 角度看 $p$ 值",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            144,
            463,
            244
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "考虑 $\\bar{y}^{\\mathrm{rep}}$ 与 $\\bar{y}$ 的大小关系：由于 $\\bar{y}^{\\mathrm{rep}}$ 是 $\\theta_0$ 的“代表值”， $\\bar{y}$ 是 $\\theta$ 的“代表值”。",
        "bbox": [
            79,
            314,
            893,
            500
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "list",
        "sub_type": "text",
        "list_items": [
            "若 $\\mathrm{H}_{0}$ 成立（ $\\theta = \\theta_{0}$ ），则可以预计： $P(\\overline{y}^{\\mathrm{rep}} > \\overline{y})$ 应该接近 0.5。",
            "反之，若 $P(\\bar{y}^{\\mathrm{rep}} > \\bar{y})$ 接近 0 或接近 1；则认为 $\\mathrm{H}_{0}$ 不成立。"
        ],
        "bbox": [
            66,
            585,
            892,
            801
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "统计量的引入",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            94,
            142,
            396,
            235
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/9f954f4207ffa587b4e004adb9a06a82f656e2c46cb657be73023bc86eb00242.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            83,
            277,
            918,
            875
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "单边检验",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            142,
            296,
            235
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "list",
        "sub_type": "text",
        "list_items": [
            "若此概率接近0，则拒绝 $\\mathrm{H}_{0}$ 。进一步， $P\\{N(0,1) > T(y)\\} \\approx 0$ ，由于 $\\bar{y}^{\\mathrm{rep}} > \\bar{y}$ 为小概率事件，故认为 $\\theta_{0}< \\theta$ ，即 $\\mathrm{H}_{1}: \\theta > \\theta_{0}$ 成立。",
            "若此概率接近1，则拒绝 $\\mathrm{H}_{0}$ 。进一步， $P\\{N(0,1) > T(y)\\} \\approx 1$ 等价于 $P\\{N(0,1) < T(y)\\} \\approx 0$ 。由于 $\\bar{y}^{\\mathrm{rep}} < \\bar{y}$ 为小概率事件，故认为 $\\theta_{0} > \\theta$ ，即 $\\mathrm{H}_{1}: \\theta < \\theta_{0}$ 成立。"
        ],
        "bbox": [
            20,
            277,
            486,
            912
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$p$ 值计算公式:",
        "bbox": [
            529,
            274,
            685,
            329
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} \\triangleright H _ {1} \\colon \\theta > \\theta_ {0} \\colon p _ {c} = P \\{N (0, 1) > T (y) \\} \\\\ \\triangleright H _ {1} \\colon \\theta <   \\theta_ {0} \\colon p _ {c} = P \\{N (0, 1) <   T (y) \\} \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            531,
            377,
            947,
            535
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "若 $p_{c}< \\alpha$ （接近0），则拒绝 $\\mathrm{H}_{0}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            531,
            661,
            875,
            718
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "双边检验",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            142,
            296,
            233
        ],
        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "对 $H_{1}: \\theta \\neq \\theta_{0}$ , 则需要",
        "bbox": [
            63,
            318,
            345,
            379
        ],
        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\nP \\{N (0, 1) > T (y) \\} \\approx 0 \\quad {\\text {或}} \\quad P \\{N (0, 1) <   T (y) \\} \\approx 0\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            168,
            464,
            825,
            527
        ],
        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "注：两者只能其中一个发生",
        "bbox": [
            61,
            609,
            419,
            666
        ],
        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "双边检验",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            144,
            296,
            235
        ],
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1. 若 $P\\{N(0,1) > T(y)\\} \\approx 0$ , 则可知 $T(y) > 0$ , 因此",
        "bbox": [
            66,
            314,
            751,
            387
        ],
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n0 \\approx P \\{N (0, 1) > T (y) \\} = P \\{N (0, 1) > | T (y) | \\}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            211,
            464,
            775,
            531
        ],
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "2. 若 $P\\{N(0,1) < T(y)\\} \\approx 0$ ，则可知 $T(y) < 0$ ，因此",
        "bbox": [
            63,
            607,
            743,
            677
        ],
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n0 \\approx P \\{N (0, 1) <   T (y) \\} = P \\{N (0, 1) > - T (y) \\} = P \\{N (0, 1) > | T (y) | \\}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            71,
            757,
            926,
            827
        ],
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "双边检验",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            144,
            296,
            235
        ],
        "page_idx": 10
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "综合1.和2.可得： $p = 2P\\{N(0,1) > |T(y)|\\}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            62,
            316,
            603,
            387
        ],
        "page_idx": 10
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$p$ 值计算公式:",
        "bbox": [
            62,
            496,
            242,
            559
        ],
        "page_idx": 10
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\triangleright H _ {1} \\colon \\theta \\neq \\theta_ {0} \\colon p _ {c} = P \\{| N (0, 1) | > | T (y) | \\} = 2 P \\{N (0, 1) > | T (y) | \\}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            67,
            614,
            881,
            677
        ],
        "page_idx": 10
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "若 $p_{c}< \\alpha$ （接近0），则拒绝 $\\mathrm{H}_{0}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            63,
            800,
            462,
            862
        ],
        "page_idx": 10
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "概率的另一个方向",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            96,
            144,
            490,
            235
        ],
        "page_idx": 11
    },
    {
        "type": "list",
        "sub_type": "text",
        "list_items": [
            "$\\succ$ 若 $\\mathrm{H}_{0}$ 成立（ $\\theta = \\theta_{0}$ ），则可以预计： $P(\\bar{y}^{\\mathrm{rep}} < \\bar{y})$ 应该接近 0.5。",
            "反之，若 $P(\\bar{y}^{\\mathrm{rep}} < \\bar{y})$ 接近 0 或接近 1；则认为 $\\mathrm{H}_{0}$ 不成立。"
        ],
        "bbox": [
            66,
            314,
            893,
            529
        ],
        "page_idx": 11
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "思考: 根据 $P\\left(\\bar{y}^{\\text {rep}} < \\bar{y}\\right)$ 是否可以得到如上的推导?",
        "bbox": [
            77,
            766,
            901,
            851
        ],
        "page_idx": 11
    }
]